    MG Wallet Account Terms of Use and Agreement
    IMPORTANT -- PLEASE READ: The following MG Wallet Agreement describes the terms and conditions that apply to the stored value account of your MG Wallet. This agreement is divided into two parts. Part One describes the terms that apply generally to the MG Wallet. Part Two contains important legal terms and conditions.
