    PART ONE: MG Wallet GENERAL TERMS
    About Your Account;  MG Super Charge Stations Purchases Only
    The MG Wallet allows you to load a monetary value onto your MG Wallet for future using MG Super Charge stations' charging service and related services in Thailand. The MG Wallet is to be treated like cash. No refund is available for the MG Wallet except as required by law. The monetary value that you load onto your MG Wallet is a pre-payment only for the goods and services of participating MG Super Charge stations. No credit card, credit line, overdraft protection or deposit account is associated with an MG Wallet. No interest, dividends or any other earnings on funds loaded onto an MG Wallet will accrue or be paid or credited to you by us. The value associated with the MG Wallet is not insured or guaranteed by any person or entity. The monetary value stored on any MG Wallet may not be transferred to another MG Wallet.
    Your MG Wallet is valid for use in participating MG Super Charge stations in Thailand only. We reserve the right not to accept any MG Wallet or otherwise limit use of an MG Wallet if we reasonably believe that the use is unauthorized, fraudulent or otherwise unlawful.
    Loading Value on Your Card
    You can only load value onto an MG Wallet in MG iSMART mobile APP to your mobile phone device (Android™ or IOS).
    The value of your MG Wallet is subject to the following load limits: the minimum amount that can be loaded is THB 200 and the maximum balance amount is THB 10,000. We may change the minimum amounts at any time by notifying on the MG iSMART mobile app and such change shall not constitute an amendment to this agreement.
    Fees and Expiry Date
    We do not charge any fees for the issuance, activation, use or reloading of your MG Wallet. Your MG Wallet has no expiration date.
    Receipts and Statements
    MG Wallet owners are not sent statements of itemized transactions from an MG Wallet account. You can check the balance of your MG Wallet or review recent transaction records on your MG iSMART mobile app or by calling 02-114-7638.
    Redemption
    Any amount on your MG Wallet is non-refundable, non-transferable and may not be exchanged for cash or credit balance unless required by law or permitted by the terms of this agreement. All reward or promotional benefits are valid only within their stipulated periods.
    Complaint Handling
    We reserve the right to correct the balance of your MG Wallet account if we believe that a clerical, billing or accounting error has occurred. If you have questions regarding your transaction history or any correction, or if you dispute any transaction or correction that has been assessed against your MG Wallet, please contact our Customer Care Team by phone at 02-114-7638 and we will conduct an investigation and communicate the results and correct any error that we verify as soon as we finish the investigation. If no error was found, we will communicate an explanation.
    Optional Registration; Liability for Unauthorized Transactions
    Because your MG Wallet is used like cash for purchases from MG Super Charge stations, you are responsible for all transactions associated with your MG Wallet, including unauthorized transactions.
    PART TWO: IMPORTANT LEGAL TERMS
    Changes to This Agreement
    We may amend the terms of this agreement at any time for security, legal, regulatory or valid business reasons. We will post the terms to the modified agreement on MG iSMART mobile APP. Subject to the remainder of this clause, any change, addition or deletion will become effective at the time we post the revised agreement to MG iSMART mobile APP. Unless we state otherwise, the change, addition or deletion will apply to your MG Wallet. The amended terms will apply to you if (a) you do not notify us in writing to the contrary within twenty (20) days of the date of our notice (or such other reasonable period of time as specified in our notice to you), or (b) you use your MG Wallet after such twenty (20) day notice period. If you do not accept the changes, additions or deletions, you should stop using the MG Wallet.
